data.title: Fishing Derby - Boy Scouts of America
data.meta_description: Information about Fishing Derby from The Lincoln Heritage Council - Boy Scouts of America.
data.meta_site_name: Lincoln Heritage Council - Boy Scouts of America
data.text:
The Fishing Derby is a great time for our Cub Scouts to come out and see if they can catch the biggest fish of the day!

BUT wait, thereâ€™s more! Along with fishing, Cub Scouts will also be able to participate in many other events such as, BBs, archery, crafts, science experiments and so much more!

We encourage our Packs to come out and camp with us for the weekend but you are more than welcome to just come to the event for a day!

All Cub Scouts will receive a patch, a mess kit and a weekend full of fun adventures!

REGISTER HERE

To reserve your campsite, please contact Rebecca Skees at r.skees87@gmail.com
